reviewText: can not get it to play on desktop/ Laptop????
Bought as Christmas present for my dad & he loved it!
Love it as myself a SEABEE ,,,
Got when expected. No complaints. It was a gift.
My fiance was a SeaBee and he thoroughly enjoyed watching this movie.
Thought this would be more modern on today's SeaBees. Although informative, I was hoping for more present information on how the SeaBees interact in today's military. I'll keep looking.
Excellent WWII information on Seabees. Almost none on Korea. And as a Seabee with 3 tours in Vietnam I was not surprised that we were over looked again.

I received the video within a very short period of time.

I watched this with my 78 year old Seabee and it took him right back with the great footage. THis video includes facts about how they came to be.  I enjoyed watching it very much.  I wish it was longer.
